.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-2::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: gardening, hiking, reading, skydiving, writing
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: country, d&b, disco, r&b, techno
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: orchid, daffodil, aconite, amaryllis, balloon-flower
The people use 5 different means of transport: helicopter, quad-bike, roller, scooter, skateboard
 1. the person driving the skateboard is in the middle##1
 2. the fan of techno is on the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
 3. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
 4. the person who's hobby is writing is on the right of the person who growsdaffodil##1
 5. the person driving the quad-bike is between the person who growsorchid and the fan of techno##2
 6. the person driving the scooter is the person who's hobby is hiking##1
 7. the fan of country is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1
 8. the person who growsaconite is the fan of r&b##1
 9. the person who growsaconite is on the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
10. the fan of disco is on the right of the fan of d&b##1
11. the person who growsaconite is the person who's hobby is reading##1
12. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the person who growsballoon-flower##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |     3      |    4    |     5      |
| Hobby         | skydiving | gardening | writing    | hiking  | reading    |
| Music-Genre   | techno    | d&b       | disco      | country | r&b        |
| Flower   | balloon-flower   | daffodil     | orchid    | amaryllis  | aconite     |
| Transport     | roller    | quad-bike | skateboard | scooter | helicopter |

