.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-3::.
There are 5 different nationalities: malaysian, australian, thai, french, chinese
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: adventure, documentary, family, martial-arts, superhero
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: ambient, gospel, metal, pop, reggae
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: badminton, basketball, rowing, tennis, volleyball
 1. the chinese is the fan of gospel##1
 2. the person who's sport is tennis is in the middle##1
 3. the fan of pop is in the middle##1
 4. the person watching adventure movies is in the middle##1
 5. the chinese is on the right of the person who's sport is basketball##1
 6. the australian is on the left of the fan of ambient##1
 7. the fan of reggae is on the left of the person who's sport is rowing##1
 8. the person watching adventure movies is on the right of the person watching documentary movies##1
 9. the fan of metal is on the far left##1
10. the person who's sport is badminton is the person watching martial-arts movies##1
11. the thai is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
12. the french is on the right of the fan of reggae##1
13. the person who's sport is volleyball is between the person watching superhero movies and the thai##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4       |       5       |
| Nationality         | malaysian | chinese     | thai   | australian   | french |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero  | documentary | adventure | martial-arts | family        |
| Music-Genre   | metal      | gospel      | pop       | reggae       | ambient       |
| Sport         | basketball | volleyball  | tennis    | badminton    | rowing        |

