 4. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the french##1
 5. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
 6. the person drinking water is between the person watching zombie movies and the person who's hobby is fishing##2
 7. the person who's hobby is collecting is the turkish##1
 8. the australian is on the far right##1
 9. the person watching sports movies is on the right of the french##1
10. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the far right##1
11. the person watching thriller movies is between the person watching zombie movies and the person who's hobby is fishing##2
